# Agent continuation guide — pheno-harness

Read this before any multi-step work. Specs live in `agileplus-specs/` (AgilePlus intent model).

## North star

**Accepted verified steps / sec / GB / $** — not raw tok/s. See `config/eval_pillars.yaml` and SPEC-005.

## Cloud model (2026-06)

- **Firepass Kimi is sunset** — do not route TB2 or routine work through Fireworks fpk.
- **OmniRoute `Main` combo** is the primary cloud worker: one OpenAI-compatible endpoint blending Claude Max, OpenAI Codex/Chat, MiniMax M3, and local 3090 tiers via subscription quotas.
- Forge / agent-runner use `OPENAI_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:20128/v1`, model **`Main`**. Never override `OPENAI_*` in harness scripts.

## Hardware

- **1× RTX 3090 Ti (24 GB)** for training and local inference only.
- Burst 5090 / multi-GPU deferred unless spec explicitly approves.

## Safety

- **Risky-action gate always on** for agents with shell access: `config/risky_action_gate.yaml`, `verifier/risky_action.py`.
- Activation edits (abliteration, DFlash drafts) never bypass pre-execution verification.

## Key commands

```powershell
cd C:\Users\koosh\pheno-harness
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Specs index
type agileplus-specs\index\spec.md

# Eval suite
python scripts/collect_traces.py
python scripts/analyze_wastage.py
python scripts/run_eval_suite.py --small-grid

# Harbor TB2 (OmniRoute Main)
python scripts/probe_omniroute_models.py --force
python scripts/run_tbench_route_matrix.py --route-kind omniroute_combo --pilot --force

# Local model / decode / MoE gates
python scripts/list_local_bench_candidates.py
python scripts/decode_prepare.py list
python scripts/moe_prepare.py list
python scripts/activation_prepare.py list
```

